OL,3,CMet chief: Violence against women
OL,4,Cshould be treated the 'same as
OL,5,Cterrorism'
OL,7,F"The aim nationally should be to treat
OL,8,Fit as a national security threat like
OL,9,Fwe treat organised crime, like we
OL,10,Ftreat terrorism," he said.
OL,12,F"When you look at the amount of harm
OL,13,Fthat predatory men create in
OL,14,Fcommunities and to individuals, that's
OL,15,Fwhat it deserves."
