OL,7,FHe said that while 34,000 men had
OL,8,Fallegations made against them in one
OL,9,Fyear in London, figures from the
OL,10,Fannual Crime Survey for England and
OL,11,FWales suggest nationally 800,000 women
OL,12,Fhave been sexually assaulted.
OL,14,FSeparate estimates from the National
OL,15,FCrime Agency suggest that 750,000 men
OL,16,Fpose a sexual threat to children.
OL,18,FSir Mark said: "You start to add these
OL,19,Fnumbers together. There are a lot of
OL,20,Fmen who are a threat to women and
OL,21,Fchildren.
OL,26,@zD@POU
