OL,7,FSir Mark faced questioning by the
OL,8,Fboard in the wake of the first part of
OL,9,Fthe Angiolini Inquiry published last
OL,10,Fweek, which found that killer officer
OL,11,FWayne Couzens was a serial sexual
OL,12,Fpredator who should never have been
OL,13,Femployed by the police service.
OL,15,FCouzens was able to work for three
OL,16,Fdifferent forces despite a 20-year
OL,17,Fhistory of sexual depravity and
OL,18,Fspiralling debts, which should have
OL,19,Fstopped him being a police officer.
