OL,7,FInstead he abused his powers to kidnap
OL,8,Fand then rape and murder marketing
OL,9,Fexecutive Sarah Everard as she walked
OL,10,Fhome from a friend's house in Clapham,
OL,11,Fsouth London, in March 2021.
OL,13,FLondon Mayor Sadiq Khan began the
OL,14,Fmeeting by expressing his "deepest
OL,15,Fsympathies" to her loved ones, and
OL,16,Flabelling Lady Elish Angiolini's
OL,17,Freport "one of the most shattering
OL,18,Faccounts of failure in British
OL,19,Fpolicing history".
